Types of Enterprise Java Beans:
There are two main types of  EJBs
1- Session Beans
2- Message Driven Beans

1- Session Beans
Stateful  Session Bean
----------------------
-Shopping Cart
-Is tied to particular client always.

Stateless Session Bean
-They wont store clients Conversational State. After processing ones client request, if the next 
request comes,again new bean will process this request.

Single tone Session Bean
-Single instacne will be created for entire application and its shared across all applications.

When to Use Enterprise Java Beans EJB

